Author: Titans
Full.Text: This laptop is really nice and has great specs for sure. The problem is the display is AWFUL! It's is really faded and washed out looking. I have had 720p resolution Chromebooks that had a much, much better display than this HP laptop. Obviously, HP cut corners on the display to bring the price down and it's too bad. I tried everything HP suggested to fix the display (update graphics drivers, etc, etc), but nothing worked. Also, the laptop does not have where the charging is limited to a certain amount if you keep it plugged in all the time (to preserve the battery life long term). For example, my Asus laptop has it where charging is limited to 60% and my battery life is 91% after three years so the Asus' battery charking limiting software definitely works. I returned this HP laptop.

Author: Titans
Full.Text:
funnyjoke said: I want to use my DAP for the same purpose - only to stream. Can you confirm if the audio quality is better while streaming Spotify through a DAP like the M1S as compared to just normally playing it from your smartphone via wired headphones? Click to expand... There is no headphone port on iPhone, so it depends what USB DAC are you using.
Shanling said: Yes, it can connect to iPhones, iPads, Macs. I believe your only issue is with the Apple TV Bluetooth, correct? Please what cable you used for connection? We will check on it when we are back in office in second half of February. Click to expand... hello. thank you for your quick response. Dont get me wrong, i love this product and just want to get the best out of it. its a very capable product but some of the problems make it useless in my case. Yes if someone uses it as a tidal streamer or dap, maybe there are no issues there. But still its 2024, so no BT connection with probably the BEST tv box (not just a no-name product) + no bt connection with a recent flagship OLED LG TV is not acceptable. I have used more than 10 different cables all apple usb c cables (braded and the normal one) baseus, satechi, 10 gbps etc. when connected to macbook no problem when connected to iphone/ipad no matter what quality is the song using apple music, the quality on the display is the same. not only that its on 32bit always even if its 16 or 24 bit. It shouldnt be so difficult for your team to reproduce the unit not connected to apple tv box 4k... should be really an easy fix and it has been so many months since i reported this issue to you. hope you take it into consideration. regards

Also upgraded. Still no luck connecting to my apple tv 4k via bt and bt connection with my oled lg TV is so out of sync so I can't use it. This is really bad for a product at this price tag. Can anyone answer if the digital filters are working over wifi/Bluetooth/USB dac mode or is it only for the built-in music player?
Shanling said: That is response we received from software team. As they don't have access to Apple TV Box right now, troubleshooting the Bluetooth issue make take some time. Software team currently has no plans to pursue Airplay 2 support. Click to expand... Hello. is there any update on this? Can you PLEASE make this unit just connect via BLUETOOTH to one of the most popular tv boxes in the worl? Apple tv 4k? there is just a message with a password, i press accept, nothing happens, there is an automatic second try after a few seconds, new password and it fails again. On the LG tv it can connect via SBC HD but the audio it out of sync and the built in tv adjustment is not active with this unit. the unit is useless using one of its key functions, BT/airplay connection. please escalate this. regards, christos

Full.Text:
babarrun said: Hi Titans, thanks for your details reply. just some clarifications: in 2) you mention "connect your M1s to iPhone/iPad/MacBook etc" - do you mean connect by wire? if yes which cable are you using? in 4) you mention "if I haven't enabled the AptX HD from the iPhone app and even I have LDAC selected from the M1s, Momentum 4 connect with AptX HD". to my knowledge the iPhone can only use AAC or SBC codecs and not AptX HD. With this in mind are you stating that you have selected the M1s bluetooth codec from an app within the iPhone? I was trying the creative W5 earlier today but the disturbance was quite high with crackling, losses of the song etc. This would be a huge deal for me if I can play tidal / Apple Music etc from my iPhone to my LDAC or APTx HD to my bt headsets. I just want to be 100% want to be sure as I have invested a few hundred in dongles and the hiBy r2 which was promised as a fix. At the end of the day I want to use this device as a DAC and a Bluetooth transmitter. I don't care for any other built in features and I will never put in a memory card to play music as I stream everything and that which I have encoded is all in ALAC which requires an Apple Music player. Click to expand... yes my "bad" 1) I mean by cable, as you can only use either receive or transmit BT on the M1s. so you basically connect the m1s by wire to iPhone/iPad/MacBook and by BT with any BT and using a variety of hq codecs 2) there is an app for the sennheisers and most of the bt headsets. to connect via hq codecs you usually need to enable this feature as it provides a less stable connection to the majority of users might prefer the stability over the quality that their source won't provide in the first place. connect via wire ----> connect via BT to any headset / bt enabled amp ---> enjoy ldac/aptx hd instead of just AAC
Shanling said: That is response we received from software team. As they don't have access to Apple TV Box right now, troubleshooting the Bluetooth issue make take some time. Software team currently has no plans to pursue Airplay 2 support. Click to expand... M1s is a product that retails more than a Apple TV box. this is kind of embarrassing for your company. you cant really reply something like this in public. just buy an Apple TV box, or maybe we can supply one for your team?...

Full.Text: "We'd always try and get up there on the summer when they're going through training camp. It was cool to see the inside. I definitely envisioned myself playing there, and putting on that two-tone blue." #Titans Select UT-Martin WR Colton Dowell in the Seventh Round of NFL Draft

Author: Titans
Full.Text: "I had a great time talking with everybody, the whole staff, coaches, player personnel people and everything. It was a great visit all-around. I enjoyed being in Tennessee." #Titans Select Maryland OT Jaelyn Duncan in Sixth Round of NFL Draft

Author: Titans
Full.Text: "When that call came, I don't even know if he could understand what I was saying. My heart was pounding. We're both just excited for me to get down there and contribute any way I can to the team." #Titans Select Cincinnati TE Josh Whyle in Fifth Round of NFL Draft

Author: Titans
Full.Text: "He can run between the tackles. He's elusive, and he can make guys miss as well as contribute in the passing game. Just another guy who can do it all for us, and you can put him in the game in any situation." #Titans Select Tulane RB Tyjae Spears in the Third Round of NFL Draft

Author: Titans
Full.Text: "I stayed positive, and I knew what was meant to be, was going to happen. When I saw they traded up for me, that alone was telling me that they wanted me, they wanted this to happen." #Titans Select QB Will Levis in Second Round of NFL Draft

Full.Text:
SAFETY RECALL 23TA03 Certain 2022-2023 Tundra HV Certain 2022-2023 Tundra Tonneau Cover May Come Off While Driving Q4: When will the remedy become available? A4: Toyota is currently preparing the remedy. At this time, Toyota estimates the remedy can be available in a few months, but this timing is subject to change. https://pressroom.toyota.com/toyota-recalls-certain-2022-and-2023-tundra-models/
For anyone wondering how, on mine the hardware on the front mounts loosen on dirt roads or anything bumpy. The sliding attachment on the front also doesn’t seem to hold it enough even with the hardware being tightened. Mine slid 4-5 inches off to the right side when I noticed it first and had to take it off.

Full.Text: I would ask to see the employment contract where it states she has to return the sign on bonus if she left. Companies will use pressure tactics to get you to pay back. Just like how they pressure you to sign on the dotted line in order for you to receive severance when being laid off. See this all the time on Wall Street so I wouldn’t pay anything back until they can prove she agreed to that before starting the job. Good luck.

Author: Titans
Full.Text: Hi - I am very new to this! My sister was diagnosed with terminal cancer around 3 months ago - prognosis is less that 12 months. She has always been a very self sufficient and capable woman, always active and very sociable... which has now all gone - not through lack of trying, she just physically cannot sustain the life she used to have. Her husband is very supportive and very patient with her which takes away so much worry we have for her and her well being. But she has hit a wall the last week or so mentally, coming to terms with it all and processing the timeline she is facing. The anger and frustration at the situation has really taken over. She has so much support from her partner, but I want to know from the perspective of those in this situation what can I do to help in this situation? I know I can't fix it, but what support should I be offering? What shouldn't I be doing? I would never want her to feel pitied or that she is a burden, I just want to be able to offer support or even just distraction that she may not feel comfortable to ask for or maybe even not know to ask for? Any advice/suggestions would be appreciated :)
